window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After gaining epic power and knowledge, Alex Roth will confront Uldar’s legacy and face the Ravener once and for all.</b><br> <br> A cycle of victory and horror: the pride of the Kingdom of Thameland.<br> <br> That is the Ravener’s cycle.<br> <br> Over years of study, Alex Roth is finally an archwizard, has overcome the Mark of the Fool, and empowered his friends and companions. Yet their foe is the mightiest they have faced yet: the Ravener itself, now freed from thousands of years of chains and returned to its full strength.<br> <br> Alex will need to call on all his magic, all his bonds, his wits, his strategy and his resources to not only destroy the Ravener, but to shatter the cycle that has chained his kingdom since time immemorial.<br> <br> And Alex plans to destroy the hell out of it.</p> <p><b>The epic finale of the Best-Selling series. Finish your fantastical journey into a coming-of-age magic academy fantasy with a weak-to-strong progression into power, deepening mystery, a setting inspired by D&amp;D, detailed world building and magical science, action, comedy, slice-of-life, and GameLit elements.</b></p>"; 
